**Simplified text:**

I love collecting things. It is a world of passion, envy and enthusiasm. If you enter this world, remember one thing: you must fall in love with the object before you collect it. People have been collecting things since the beginning of time. They collect stones, seashells, flowers, paintings and other things. I have been collecting all my life. I have collected flowers, pottery, paintings and other things. My first collection was of stones picked up in my parents' garden. I was fascinated by these objects. I am not alone in being interested in collecting objects. One in three adults indulges the same passion. If you want to start a collection, you do not have to be rich or powerful. You can start with small objects, like flowers or coins. You can also collect things that are important to you, like family photos or souvenirs from your travels.<eos>
